          베이비시터 & 보모 서비스
        </h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-8">
          엄마의 사랑으로 아이를 돌보는 전문 베이비시터
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Infants 0-2 -->
        <div class="bg-[#fff7f4] rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-[#D37643] font-bold text-xl mb-4">영유아 (0-2세)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>수유 및 이유식 준비</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>젖병 소독 및 관리</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>기저귀 교체 및 위생 관리</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>목욕 및 수면 관리</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>아기 세탁물 관리</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Children 3+ -->
        <div class="bg-[#fff7f4] rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-[#D37643] font-bold text-xl mb-4">유아 및 학령기 (3세 이상)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>식사 준비 및 제공</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>교육적 놀이 활동</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>목욕 (선택 사항)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>학교 등하원 픽업</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>숙제 도움</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
