              <span>주방 청소 및 설거지</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Cleaning Services -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-[#D37643] font-bold text-lg mb-4">청소 서비스</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>집/사무실 청소</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>이사 전후 청소</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>대청소 서비스</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>화장실/주방 집중 청소</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Meal Preparation -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-[#D37643] font-bold text-lg mb-4">식사 준비</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>천연 조미료 사용</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>한식 및 양식 조리</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
              <span>밑반찬 준비</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D37643] mr-2">•</span>
